“A stranger tale I’ve heard is that go deeper in, deeper down the black seas, and you’ll end up seeing another Sun! Another bloody Sun if you can believe that! Well, the folk I’ve heard it from ended up being a deranged lunatic murderer.”
“But hey—what do I know? I’m just a barkeep. Could be half these tales are old miners’ drink-talk…
…or maybe the Underdark really is a cathedral of endless night, and those chrome elves are listenin’ to us right now.”
He tops off your mugs and winks.
“If you’re fool enough to go lookin’, best bring more than courage.
